5.title: Home
5.content: The theoretical component of my research relates the computational complexity law to the evolution of topological properties in biological networks. The experimental component involves experimental methods in the areas of DNA/RNA computing and DNA nanotechnology. . . (this site is being actively updated, some links/sections are still WIP) .
